data.description: Prime land and country life in the city, almost 2 and half acres. Perfect for self-employed buyer who needs lots of room to run and store items. Four bedrooms, huge diving pool, hot tub, deck, beautiful covered outdoor living space for entertaining, outdoor kitchen, outdoor fireplace and built in sand play area. Huge game room opens up to backyard. Huge barn, RV hook ups on site. Two smaller sheds stay. Chicken coop in back used as garden area at this time. Home completely redone few years ago and is considered a permanent single family structure with traditional mortgage, qualifies for FHA, Conventional and VA. Can use same mortgage co to streamline loan process. Home's utilities are very low, property set for running home business, high speed internet. Cut your storage fees, run your business, raise chickens, plant garden, plenty of space.  One frig stays, washer dryer, office furniture, some game room, shop items, some outdoor furniture negotiable with acceptable offer. Make offer!
